    "body": "## Summary\n\n- Remove the `RewriteWgmmaSync` transform pass, which is no longer needed.\n- Delete `src/transform/wgmma_sync_rewriter.cc`, its Python wrapper in `tilelang/transform/__init__.py`, and the call site in `tilelang/engine/phase.py` (along with the now-unused `is_hopper` import).\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] Build tilelang and confirm compilation succeeds without the removed source file.\n- [ ] Run existing Hopper (sm90+) GEMM tests to ensure wgmma code generation still works correctly.\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n## Release Notes\n\n* **Chores**\n  * Removed an optimization pass that previously rewrote synchronization operations for GPU memory operations. This may affect performance characteristics on certain hardware targets.\n\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
